                            <p class="lead subheader-text"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span> How To Play</p>
                            <p>
                                Download the game at the Download Page to start a match with 3 other players. Log into an existing account and click the Join Lobby button. When all four players are ready, the game will automatically begin. There are a total of 4 players in a single game, consisting of teams of two.
                                Work with your teammate to dominate your opponents.
                                <br /><br />
                                Each player is allocated a set amount of resources. Players obtain resources by destroying enemy viruses. Build towers to defend yourself while your viruses attack the enemy towers and work towards the enemy's anti-virus.
                                <br /><br />The game is over once the enemy's anti-virus is destroyed.
                            </p>
                        </div>
