                                <br /><br /><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-minus subheader-text"></span> Each structures have their own strengths and weaknesses. Use a combination to create a winning strategy.
                                <br /><br /><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-minus subheader-text"></span> Plan and work together with your teammate to conquer your enemies
                                <br /><br /><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-minus subheader-text"></span> Place towers that cover the largest area to maximize damage.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

